data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Welcome to this beautiful and spacious home inside Bentwood Ranch. This gorgeous, well kept home is located near bases, great schools, and shopping in a family friendly neighborhood complete with a community pool, park, and playground. Stretch out and enjoy multiple living areas! Great open flowing floor plan features formal dining space, & large family room Entertain with ease utilizing the open kitchen area featuring an island , breakfast area, huge walk-in pantry and cabinets galore. Plenty of updates, including new flooring and fresh paint throughout! Large master suite, complete with a sizable bathroom containing a double vanity, separate shower and tub and huge naturally lit walk-in closet. Huge game room or extra living area or office space, utility sink, water softener, plenty of closets, over extended patio perfect for BBQ's in a beautifully landscaped backyard. Definitely a must see!!!
